&lt;li&gt;Directly manage the email strategy, including list segmentation, automation, and editing in collaboration with the Associate Director of Digital Engagement.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Vision and project manage the Party at the Polls website, ensuring a seamless user experience for voters and partners.&lt;/li&gt;
