&lt;li&gt;Develop comprehensive digital toolkits for community partners, providing them with the assets and guidance needed to activate their local networks.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide technical assistance to partners to help them promote their parties using digital platforms.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Oversee the video strategy for Party at the Polls, ensuring high-quality storytelling that highlights flagship events and partner success stories.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stay up-to-date with current trends and techniques, sharing information and inspiration with digital team members.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as the editor for all direct voter contact materials, ensuring tone, brand consistency, and clarity.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analyze digital performance metrics and update strategy based on real-time voter and partner behavior.&lt;/li&gt;
